{"tid":366615,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙學最新指示】岑敖暉：現在使用武力反抗具正當性！","createTime":"2017-08-20T07:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T09:31:06.000Z","uid":79563,"like":78,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e09acc0f41dd198a9c90c481f3fd917f062ab09","tid":366615,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/deueeo3xf/TVB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2Fdeueeo3xf%2FTVB.jpg&h=99e4f297&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全片 (絕無無斷章取義)：<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/59991fcee60383050e701379\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F59991fcee60383050e701379&d=DsmaqcTzu27K8cC6FG0AyLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=48383cac\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/59991fcee60383050e701379</a><br />\n<br />\n兩宗非法集會案的十六人被改判即時監禁，學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉指無悔這樣做，又指若壓迫愈大，暴力反抗亦變得有正當性。<br />\n<br />\n兩宗非法集會案，三名前學生領袖及反新界東北發展的十三人，因律政司申請覆核刑期，先後被改判即時監禁，學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉在本台節目《講清講楚》指，新的刑期是意料之外，因為以往初犯的同類案件，就算判監都是以星期計。他認為就算知道刑期加重，亦無悔這樣做。<br />\n<br />\n學聯前副秘書長岑敖暉表示：「在制度下用盡所有最溫和合法手段爭取民主，依然未有足夠人數去撼動這個政權時，我們希望跳出原本框框。我覺得視乎影響多少不同人的權利，當我們見到整個社會制度，很大規模我們經濟平等權利，資源分配權利、政治權利，人權集會自由權利，可能這數年中央影響很明確，這些空間收窄很要緊。」<br />\n<br />\n被問到當日的行為會否影響其他年輕人，岑敖暉指社會的反抗力度是取決於有多大壓迫：「政權將幾大壓迫放在我們年輕人或者抗爭者身上，就會自然相應引發多大壓迫出來。我認為當政權壓迫越來越大，人民反抗力度越大，這絕對有正當性。」<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉承認2014年佔領行動後，香港民主運動踏入低潮，但今次裁決不會影響日後參與的人數，反而成為他們的「強心針」。"},{"pid":"443fda68fd9861e34eeffcbf2a95c416b240a1ec","tid":366615,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f9df53cb62992e733bafb9797b3e96695d5f99","tid":366615,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"終於等到雙學ENDORSE比光環啦！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a9729b71316c2fc2eeeb042e655c51c9cd1484","tid":366615,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/20/151211_b8091bdb63d83e48439bab62bf9d96b0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F20%2F151211_b8091bdb63d83e48439bab62bf9d96b0.jpg&h=dcabc23c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"e6cdadd491b0e5fe08cfba396d61682df4569191","tid":366615,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:23:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>FUCK CHINA</strong></span>"},{"pid":"eeb2365bc6d9e9b6f618e06cf8ba0c0b9a0e6a44","tid":366615,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:24:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78baa012672b17d43029e43f791d6bc8a09c6d8","tid":366615,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:24:35.000Z","msg":"2017-08-20 13:36 最新指示 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9de3b26585f016ea13b24d4ffe42f504fe4a57","tid":366615,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:36:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc6bc76206b60b6fecae220ab55e8b926ebfbfc","tid":366615,"uid":14583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:39:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"322cde5a7c7511d5fc5f127aec6b39ba024c12ab","tid":366615,"uid":121060,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T07:42:42.000Z","msg":"佢個樣殘左咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmo